OL,3,CHow the story of Alice Ruggles is
OL,4,Cbeing used in schools to stop stalking
OL,6,FHelen Ford meets the family of Alice
OL,7,FRuggles who hope to prevent others
OL,8,Fsuffering at the hands of a stalker
OL,10,FParents on a mission to prevent the
OL,11,Fhorror and heartache they suffered at
OL,12,Flosing their child to her stalker ex-
OL,13,Fboyfriend are taking their campaign of
OL,14,Fawareness into secondary schools.
OL,16,FClive Ruggles and Sue Hills' daughter
OL,17,FAlice Ruggles was murdered in October
OL,18,F2016 at her flat following a crusade
OL,19,Fof stalking by her former partner.
