OL,3,CHow the story of Alice Ruggles is
OL,4,Cbeing used in schools to stop stalking
OL,6,FSince the death of the 24-year-old's,
OL,7,Foriginally from Leicestershire, her
OL,8,Ffamily have been educating people
OL,9,Fabout the dangers of stalking.
OL,11,FNow the charity set up in Alice's name
OL,12,Fhas joined forces withto offer
OL,13,Feducation sessions in each of the
OL,14,Fcounty's secondary schools.
OL,16,FThe aim is to help teenagers recognise
OL,17,Fthe signs of stalking - and how to
OL,18,Frespond.
