OL,3,CHow the story of Alice Ruggles is
OL,4,Cbeing used in schools to stop stalking
OL,6,FProfessor Ruggles, who founded the
OL,7,FAlice Ruggles Trust with Alice's
OL,8,Fmother and family, told ITV Tyne Tees:
OL,9,F"We want people to understand how
OL,10,Fserious stalking is and how serious
OL,11,Fthe consequences can be.
OL,13,F"But of course not all stalking
OL,14,Fescalates to the terrible end we had
OL,15,Fin Alice's case and if the right
OL,16,Fthings are done at the right time you
OL,17,Fcan prevent it getting wore and that
OL,18,F's what we have to do.
