OL,3,CHow the story of Alice Ruggles is
OL,4,Cbeing used in schools to stop stalking
OL,6,F"It's not all about protecting the
OL,7,Fvictim, though that's an important
OL,8,Fpart, it's also about dealing with the
OL,9,Fperpetrator."
OL,11,FThe short sessions will be delivered
OL,12,Fduring school assemblies across and ,
OL,13,Flargely to students from fourteen to
OL,14,Fsixteen years old.
OL,16,FThey will raise awareness of stalking
OL,17,Fand coercive behaviour - and offering
OL,18,Fpractical tools to deal with it.
