OL,3,CHow the story of Alice Ruggles is
OL,4,Cbeing used in schools to stop stalking
OL,6,FAnd while they are just 20 minutes
OL,7,Flong, those behind the project hope it
OL,8,Fwill sow the seeds in helping
OL,9,Fteenagers to recognise unhealthy
OL,10,Fbehaviours in others and themselves.
OL,12,FProfessor Ruggles said the main
OL,13,Fmessage for youngsters was that those
OL,14,Fwho recognise the signs should act on
OL,15,Fit - "don't just sit on it and let it
OL,16,Fhappen".
