OL,3,CHow the story of Alice Ruggles is
OL,4,Cbeing used in schools to stop stalking
OL,6,FHe continued: "The key message is if
OL,7,Fyou think some of these things are
OL,8,Fhappening to you or your friend and if
OL,9,Fit doesn't feel right it probably
OL,10,Fisn't right and you need to do
OL,11,Fsomething about it and there is a lot
OL,12,Fof help out there."
OL,14,FThe initiative is supported by Joy
OL,15,FAllen, Durham's Police and Crime
OL,16,FCommissioner, who told ITV Tyne Tees
OL,17,Fhow the force would respond to
OL,18,Fconcerns of stalking.
