OL,3,CHow the story of Alice Ruggles is
OL,4,Cbeing used in schools to stop stalking
OL,6,F"We've just had a dedicated stalking
OL,7,Flead put into the force," she said.
OL,8,F"One person can't achieve everything.
OL,10,F"We do, obviously, initial training on
OL,11,Fthe stalking side so the information
OL,12,Fthat they get as a new police officer,
OL,13,Fnew PCSO coming into the force, (is)
OL,14,Freally, really important but then
OL,15,Fyou've got people who've been in the
OL,16,Forganisation many, many years so we
OL,17,Fneed to cascade this training.
OL,19,F"We need to train champions across the
OL,20,Forganisation."
